data.description: Ready for Immediate Move-In! This stunning two story home boasts an open two-story foyer and a spacious gathering room complete with 2 ft extension. The kitchen is highlighted by Espresso maple cabinets with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, center island with room for seating and a walk-in pantry. The second floor features an impressive Owner's suite including double sinks, walk-in closet and shower. Generous loft area, large laundry room and 3 additional bedrooms. Other great features include a modern exterior elevation, extensive laminate wood floors on the main level, dual air conditioning units, garage door opener with keyless entry pad and professional front yard landscaping.
